node_5.description: This is carlos gomez's plan for Sunday February 09: Wake up and complete the morning routine at 7:00 am., Attend a creative writing workshop from 9:00 am to 11:00 am., Have lunch at 12:00 pm., Spend the afternoon working on the poetry collection from 1:00 pm to 4:30 pm., Eat dinner at 5:00 pm., Go for a walk to enjoy and get inspired by the natural world from 6:00 pm to 7:00 pm., Relax and read poetry from 7:30 pm to 9:00 pm., Wind down for the evening at 9:30 pm., Go to bed at 10:00 pm..
